class ASGI2Protocol(Protocol):
    def __init__(self, scope: Scope) -> None:
        ...

    async def __call__(
        self, receive: ASGIReceiveCallable, send: ASGISendCallable
    ) -> None:
        ...

        ASGISendCallable,

    Awaitable[None],
